      <title>红龙虾考虑破产以应对租赁和劳动力成本</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/red-lobster-mulls-filing-for-bankruptcy-to-fix-balance-sheet</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，海鲜连锁餐厅 Red Lobster 正在考虑根据美国破产法第 11 章申请破产，以重组其债务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/red-lobster-mulls-filing-for-bankruptcy-to-fix-balance-sheet</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 19:44:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Riot Platforms 首席执行官：比特币 ETF 是不可思议的催化剂</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-16/bitcoin-etfs-an-incredible-catalyst-riot-platforms-ceo-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Riot Platforms 首席执行官 Jason Les 表示，比特币 ETF 是一个令人难以置信的积极催化剂，并预计未来几个月比特币将出现非常积极的走势。他与 Sonali Basak 和 Tim Stenovec 就“彭博加密货币”进行了交谈。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-16/bitcoin-etfs-an-incredible-catalyst-riot-platforms-ceo-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 19:41:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
