      <title>英国寻求降息、选举、乌克兰资金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-16/uk-s-hunt-on-rate-cuts-election-ukraine-funding</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国财政大臣杰里米·亨特谈论了该国的通货膨胀、可能的降息、即将举行的选举以及为乌克兰对抗俄罗斯的战争提供资金。他在纽约接受了彭博社的 Kailey Leinz 的采访。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-16/uk-s-hunt-on-rate-cuts-election-ukraine-funding</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 19:09:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>肯·格里芬 (Ken Griffin) 押注纽约 62 层曼哈顿大厦</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-16/ken-griffin-bets-on-nyc-with-62-story-manhattan-tower-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据彭博社的 Natalie Wong 报道，肯·格里芬正在推进公园大道 62 层摩天大楼的计划，加深他对纽约市的承诺。这座塔楼的 Griffin&#39;s Citadel 和 Citadel 证券的空间至少是这两家公司目前在附近建筑中占用的空间的两倍。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-16/ken-griffin-bets-on-nyc-with-62-story-manhattan-tower-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 18:14:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>鲍威尔表示通胀意外后将推迟降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/powell-signals-high-rates-for-longer-due-to-persistent-inflation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔表示，在一系列令人惊讶的高通胀数据之后，政策制定者降息的时间将比之前预期的要长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/powell-signals-high-rates-for-longer-due-to-persistent-inflation</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 17:38:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>鲍威尔表示不急于降息后金价小幅走高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/gold-xauusd-steadies-near-record-high-with-haven-demand-fueling-rally</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着交易员消化杰罗姆·鲍威尔的言论，金价小幅走高，这表明美联储短期内没有降低利率的计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/gold-xauusd-steadies-near-record-high-with-haven-demand-fueling-rally</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 01:07:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>等待以色列对伊朗袭击做出反应，油价保持稳定</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-april-16</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于避险情绪在更广泛的市场中盛行，且交易员关注以色列对伊朗前所未有的袭击的反应，油价窄幅波动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-april-16</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 23:19:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
